
'''Toka McBaror''' ni producer wa filimi n'indirimbo muri  Nigeria, ,   <ref>https://m.guardian.ng/tag/blossom-chukwujekwu/</ref> <ref>http://www.pulse.ng/entertainment/movies/lotanna-somkhele-iyamah-adesua-etomi-adunni-ade-attend-old-school-themed-premiere-id6503121.html</ref> ndetse ajya akora nk'Umuyobozi  wa filimi   na music video <ref>https://tooxclusive.com/teni-power-rangers-prod-by-jaysynths-new-song/</ref> <ref>https://acceleratetv.com/under-the-sky-with-praise/</ref> yavutse, yazuye na ishingiye mu Kaduna, Kaduna Leta, [[Nijeriya|Nigeria]] ariko ukomoka Delta State .  Afatwa na benshi nka jack na shobuja wamayeri yose yo gukora firime nubucuruzi. Ibihembo byinshi byatsindiye, byabyaye umusaruro kandi bigamije ubuhanga bwo guhanga udushya, umutoza wo gukina amafilime akaba n'umujyanama mu bijyanye no gutunganya amafilime, McBaror avugwa cyane nka Encyclopedia of Filmmaking hamwe n'ibihembo byinshi kuri kitty ye, harimo no gutanga ibihembo kuri " Kada River " muri 2018 ''Toronto International Nollywood Film Festival'' mu canada,  <ref>https://lifestyle.thecable.ng/nollywood-travel-film-festival-movies/</ref> 6 igihembo imikino kuko filime, Lotanna harimo: ''"Best Film",'' ''"Best Director",'' ''"Best Cinematography",'' ''"Best Art Director",'' ''"Best Costume"'' no " ''Umwanditsi mwiza w'ijwi'' " muri ibihembo bya zahabu ya 2017 . <ref>https://www.sagagist.com.ng/2017/07/nollywood-director-toka-mcbaror-bags.html?m=1</ref>

Agomba kandi ibihembo bye, "Filime Nziza Nyafurika" na "Umuyobozi mwiza wa Nollywood" kuva mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filime mpuzamahanga rya Nollywood 2018, TINFF, ryabereye i Toronto, muri Kanada. <ref>https://thenationalreporterng.com/nigerian-movie-the-island-wins-best-african-film-award-at-2018-tinff/</ref> muri firime, Ikirwa, yongera gutorwa mu byiciro bya " ''Cinematografi Nziza'' " na " ''Umuyobozi mwiza'' " mu bihembo bya ZAFAA Global Awards, kubera filime ye ya Lotanna 2017. <ref>http://www.ghafla.com/gh/ghana-earns-14-nominations-2018-film-awards-london/</ref>


== Umwuga ==
Muri 2011, Mcbaror yayoboye umuririmbyi wo muri Nijeriya, amashusho y'indirimbo ya J'odie, " ''Kuchi Kuchi'' (Oh Baby)". <ref>https://www.bellanaija.com/2011/02/new-video-jodie-kuchi-kuchi-oh-baby/</ref>

Ku wa gatanu, tariki ya 10 Gashyantare 2017, yayoboye filime "Umugore wa Blogger", yasohotse muri sinema zo muri Nijeriya. Iyi filime yakozwe na Seun Oloketuyi, igaragaramo abakinnyi ba Nollywood ndetse nabakinnyi nka Segun Arinze, Adejumoke Aderounmu, Deyemi Okanlawon, Ijeoma Grace Agu na Adeniyi Johnson.  Muri 2017, filime "Kada River " yakozwe na we yatorewe igihembo mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Nollywood ryabereye i Toronto, muri Kanada. Mu bihembo bya Golden Movie 2017, yatowe mu byiciro bitandatu, birimo: " ''Filime Nziza'' ", " ''Umuyobozi mwiza'' ", " ''Sinema nziza'' ", " ''Umuyobozi w’ubuhanzi bwiza'' ", ''"Imyambarire myiza'' ", " ''Umwanditsi mwiza w’amajwi'' ".

Muri Kanama 2018, filime yayoboye yise " Ikirwa " yahawe "Filime Nziza Nyafurika" na we ubwe, "Umuyobozi wa Nollywood Nziza" mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filime mpuzamahanga rya Nollywood, TINFF, ryabereye i Toronto, muri Kanada. Muri Nzeri muri uwo mwaka, yayoboye filime, " Merry Men: The Real Yoruba Demons " ya Ayo Makun, umunyarwenya uzwi cyane wo muri Nijeriya.  Yongeye gutorwa mu byiciro bya " ''Cinematografi Nziza'' " na " ''Umuyobozi mwiza'' " muri ZAFAA Global Awards, kubera filime ye, Lotanna 2017.

Muri 2019, yasohoye igikorwa cyicyaha cya TV cyitwa, ''Paper Boat'' . 

Mu ntangiriro za 2020, yayoboye filime ya mbere y’umwaka yitwa Lilian Afegbai ''yise "Imirongo ibiri'' ". <ref>https://www.bellanaija.com/2020/02/lily-afe-double-strings-trailer/</ref> Nyuma ku ya 22 Gashyantare mu kiganiro n’abanyamakuru i [[Abuja]], yatangaje ko hagiye gukorerwa filime nshya ye yise ''Red Caravan'', azayobora kandi afatanyirize hamwe, hamwe n’ikiguzi cya N61&nbsp;miliyoni, kandi agomba kurasirwa muri Leta ya Kaduna . Filime yibanze ku gicuri kandi yashyizweho mu myaka ya 1880, mugihe ubucuruzi bwabacakara bwateye imbere kandi bugomba gukinishwa nabakinnyi nabakinnyi bagera kuri 600.  Mu gihe cya Covid-19, McBaror yasohoye urubuga rwa firime ngufi zitwa, ''The Chronicles'', zigamije gukwirakwiza abaturage ku ndwara ya Coronavirus . <ref>https://nollywoodinsider.com/toka-mcbaror-the-chronicle-short-film/</ref> 

By 2021, we mbere kugerageza ku n'ikinya movie umusaruro, filimi yise ''uhindishwa ubuzima Hano'' yari trailer yayo mugaragaro kurekurwa mu Mutarama <ref>https://www.thisdaylive.com/index.php/2021/01/23/mcbarors-creepy-lives-here-is-fearful/</ref> <ref>https://naija.yafri.ca/toka-mcbaror-taps-into-claustrophobic-dread-in-trailer-for-horror-film-creepy-lives-here/</ref> Star Afeez Oyetoro, Nancy Isime, Bimbo Ademoye ex Big Brother Naija (season 3) housemate Temidayo Adenibuyan bita Teddy A, Beverly Osu, na Mike Godson. Muri Gashyantare twabonye bwa mbere kuri Filime ya ''Underbelly'' <ref>https://www.bellanaija.com/2021/02/toka-mcbaror-underbelly-teaser/</ref> ikinamo ibikorwa bya Nollywood nka Stan Nze, Femi Adebayo, Ali Nuhu, Maryam Booth na Kunle Coker.

